        {
            "title": "九龍塘單車老翁遭小巴撞飛十多米 送院搶救不治 男司機涉危駕被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1b63816ba1d1266e43e8cec2cee9c7dc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250414/_2025041407523884430.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>九龍塘發生致命交通意外。今日（14日）清晨5時許，警方接報指一名男子在窩打老道近交限街交界，被一輛小巴撞倒昏迷不醒。救援人員送抵現場，將該名62歲男子送往醫院搶救，惟最終不治。警方初步調查後，以涉嫌「危險駕駛致他人身體嚴重受傷」將小巴男司機拘捕。\n\n</p>\n<p>消息指，涉事小巴當時由美孚前往觀塘，事發時正沿界限街東行，當駛至窩打老道橋底燈位時，撞倒一名正騎單車的男子。男子連人帶車被撞飛10多米，重傷昏迷倒臥地上。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193613/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"小巴司機涉危駕被捕。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8fc7816e36789bbd082030f13a530f2c/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-14-07-44-23_004.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        小巴司機涉危駕被捕。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193614/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7415eb71462c884f1366f4e0845d87f1/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-14-07-44-20_003.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193615/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場遺下一隻拖鞋。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3140d57a9bac197e03ccdbba8abb938c/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-14-07-44-36_008.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場遺下一隻拖鞋。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193616/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單車男捱小巴撞，送院不治。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4c882f87cd75fb2c7468711cee4e5fb2/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-14-07-44-28_006.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單車男捱小巴撞，送院不治。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4193617/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"小巴車頭損毀。蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5423fa8b2beadd3e323cd18e3159fab/2025-04/KakaoTalk_Photo_2025-04-14-07-45-11_019.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        小巴車頭損毀。蔡楚輝攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>就現場所見，小巴車頭擋風玻璃破裂，車頭凹陷。事主的單車倒在小巴後方，現場遺下一只屬於事主的拖鞋。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
